lympic committee does not'\nconceal its anxiety at those reports,\nalthough it points out that there\nis yet plenty of time for the dis\ngruntled contestant* to be pacified.\nParticularly efforts are being ma4e\nto persuade the Finnish Light-Ath\nletic* Association to change its de\ncision to abstain from the 1928 comr\npetition. Finland in 1924 piled up\na total of 166 points to America's\n255 and Great Britain\u2019s 85Vfc. Nur\nmi\u2019s track achievements igade ath\nletic history, and Olympic official*\nadmit That the little northern na\ntion\u2019s withdrawal from the 1928\ngames would be a knockout blow\nto the prospects of their success.\nSemi-Pro League Holds\nMeeting Next Monday\nThe Capital Cities Semi pro\nLeague, which appears to be hav\ning difficulties, will hold a meet\ning Monday night in what prob\nably will be the final attempt I*\neffect an organization.","height":"30542","width":"24434"}}
